{"tid":697300,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch] Splatoon 2 [61] 幾時先可以人多蝦人少","createTime":"2018-06-11T01:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T01:11:41.000Z","uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c58de4eb470e1aaddf6784e4a07fbf9c59fb709b","tid":697300,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:06:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Splatoon 2 首個付費DLC</span><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Octo Expansion</span></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/164839_7ecb0cd8095a7a41efd23bbe63666123.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F164839_7ecb0cd8095a7a41efd23bbe63666123.PNG&h=61936133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/162818_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F162818_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=75bfefbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推出日期: 2018年夏季<br />\n<br />\n價錢: US$19.99  / &yen;1800 + 稅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/164856_1d8332000ac66587ab17c8b94375f38c.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F164856_1d8332000ac66587ab17c8b94375f38c.PNG&h=a6980617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文Trailer<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jeuEcVZx0pc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjeuEcVZx0pc&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=31feeb74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jeuEcVZx0pc</a><br />\n<br />\n日文Trailer<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k2MROXA6wp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dk2MROXA6wp4&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=cf27decd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k2MROXA6wp4</a><br />\n<br />\n官方情報<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/aab6a/dlc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.co.jp%2Fswitch%2Faab6a%2Fdlc%2Findex.html&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=92133257\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/aab6a/dlc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\nDLC 內容簡介(如有任何差異一切以官方資料為準):<br />\n<br />\n追加2名新角色<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/164824_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F164824_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=8ab02788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n追加一件頭飾及一件衫<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/201318_5ddf6796287094aad22bfbf0754615fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F201318_5ddf6796287094aad22bfbf0754615fc.jpg&h=732f6262&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/201330_c1bc9525c8cbb2429ed917bf1e2dab73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F201330_c1bc9525c8cbb2429ed917bf1e2dab73.jpg&h=17bbbe3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/201332_b9ea9e6ef31c11bdc8d1cebafd89362f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F201332_b9ea9e6ef31c11bdc8d1cebafd89362f.jpg&h=f686ce3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/201334_5951516c2ec25f489198fb362fac421d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F201334_5951516c2ec25f489198fb362fac421d.jpg&h=438803b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英雄模式 追加新劇情, 80個新關卡 通關後可於對戰中操控 八爪魚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/164939_927c22d53be4c1e95520e5fa4027810e.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F164939_927c22d53be4c1e95520e5fa4027810e.PNG&h=6c8dbe75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/165433_26ef11061fce77cb3b7e1679205706c9.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F165433_26ef11061fce77cb3b7e1679205706c9.PNG&h=73f79713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/165441_754e1486a86bbf19c1367ba82eadb0a7.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F165441_754e1486a86bbf19c1367ba82eadb0a7.PNG&h=26c80c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/164947_743f044c69aa22348c16175c06e8eaac.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F164947_743f044c69aa22348c16175c06e8eaac.PNG&h=57ae1c1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/171128_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F171128_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png&h=bb9ecfc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</strong></div>"},{"pid":"340fe2a2e255cc57ad45100c1398c4c94d8532fc","tid":697300,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:06:54.000Z","msg":"[center]<img src=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/software/switch/img/panel_splatoon2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fsoftware%2Fswitch%2Fimg%2Fpanel_splatoon2.png&h=19230c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Splatoon<span style=\"color: red;\">2</span>  (スプラトゥーン<span style=\"color: red;\">2</span>)</strong></span><br />\n遊戲/Amiibo/JoyCon/ProController 發售日期：2017-7-21<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DEIEud6XoAAg-Xk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDEIEud6XoAAg-Xk.jpg&h=c9c49d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DA6zFx3XgAAoJCJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDA6zFx3XgAAoJCJ.jpg&h=dea22259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSplatoon是一款4對4 第三人稱射擊遊戲，與其他射擊遊戲有所不同<br />\n玩家需利用武器把地面塗色，佔色面積較多的一方獲勝 <br />\n<br />\n官方介紹片段(中文):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CROuiq-YjlI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCROuiq-YjlI&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=8d7f39a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CROuiq-YjlI</a><br />\n<br />\n日本官方網站:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/aab6a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.co.jp%2Fswitch%2Faab6a&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=d4e61c96\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/aab6a</a><br />\n<br />\n日本官方Twitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/splatoonjp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsplatoonjp&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=bd7fe2cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/splatoonjp</a><br />\n<br />\n香港官方網站/ 遊戲介紹:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/splatoon2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fsplatoon2&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0bdce73d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/splatoon2</a><br />\n<br />\n歐美官方網站:<br />\n<a href=\"http://splatoon.nintendo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsplatoon.nintendo.com&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f62f10b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://splatoon.nintendo.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開Post用文件<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/175OIz8UWwDI9a-EnViwmLsYUFLQItTDExKSuVRMTpdc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F175OIz8UWwDI9a-EnViwmLsYUFLQItTDExKSuVRMTpdc%2F&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=3d1a3eb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/175OIz8UWwDI9a-EnViwmLsYUFLQItTDExKSuVRMTpdc/</a>"},{"pid":"ac0d77b3b69bd81187b120a4f16064084f3373ae","tid":697300,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:07:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">常見問題/ Q&amp;A:</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nQ: 行日歐美澳版有咩分別?<br />\n<br />\nA: <br />\n行/日版 遊戲語言為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>日</strong></span>文 Splatfest(祭典)主題/時間跟日ser<br />\n歐版 遊戲語言為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英</strong></span>文 Splatfest(祭典)主題/時間跟歐ser<br />\n澳版 遊戲語言為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英</strong></span>文 Splatfest(祭典)主題/時間跟澳ser<br />\n美版 遊戲語言為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英</strong></span>文 Splatfest(祭典)主題/時間跟美ser<br />\n注意Fes活動跟據過住經驗開24小時 故不需擔心時差問題<br />\nOnline對戰<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>優先配對鄰近地區(即係亞太區)玩家</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解分咁多版?<br />\nA: 因為唔同版本Splatfest主題有唔同, 例如 午後紅茶, 變型金剛等<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點樣<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>升Rank</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 玩公開嘅網絡對戰<br />\n<br />\nQ: 去邊度玩<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>網絡對戰</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 主城直行Lobby, 或者直接撳X-&gt;A<br />\n最頂係League Battle, 同朋友組2/4人小組玩Rank Mode<br />\n第二係Rank Battle, 有3種玩法, 玩法介紹可以碌茖少少睇Q&amp;A<br />\n第三個係Turf War, 即係佔地模式<br />\n第四個係Join玩緊嘅朋友<br />\n第五係Private Match, 可以自訂Rule, 場地 同朋友玩<br />\n第六係Online Lounge, 經App voice chat+同朋友玩<br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>玩唔到網絡對戰</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 港服未開, 去<a href=\"https://accounts.nintendo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faccounts.nintendo.com&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=be87ad74\" target=\"_blank\">https://accounts.nintendo.com</a>轉region做日本/美國/歐洲, 之後重新開機<br />\n或者加多個profile, 登入日本/美國/歐洲ac, 再用該profile開game<br />\n<br />\n注: 收費服務係跟ac, 請考慮清楚用邊個ac入game<br />\n<br />\nQ: 咁唔同版本可唔可以連機?<br />\nA: 平時網絡對戰/SalmonRun可以, Splatfest活動唔得, Local面連可以<br />\n<br />\nQ: 對戰時<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>十字掣</strong></span>上下代表乜?<br />\nA:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>上</strong></span><br />\nカモン ComeOn  (平時係依個)<br />\nやられた 俾人殺咗(被殺後轉為依個)<br />\nヘルプ Help (SalmonRun死後變依個)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>下</strong></span><br />\nナイス Nice<br />\n<br />\nQ: 咩係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Splatfest(祭典)</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 玩家分兩個陣營對戰, 最後跟據表現送<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>海螺</strong></span>, 勝出隊伍會多啲海螺<br />\n海螺數目係根據你Fest完結時嘅稱號派發, 升到最高等勝出隊伍有24粒, 落敗隊伍有21粒<br />\n(稱號等級所對應海螺粒數係3-5-9-16-24/2-3-7-13-21咁上)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>稱號</strong></span>所需分數係10-25-50-99咁上, Total要184分<br />\nSplatfest只係會玩Turf War, Splatfest期間強制參加Splatfest, 無得玩Rank Mode, 但可以玩三文魚<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點參加<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Splatfest</strong></span>?<br />\nA:廣場中間告示版揀自己陣營, 揀定後會送件Fest Tee俾你, 再於指定時間(睇App,App內時間已轉換為你本地時間), 入Lobby(平時網絡對戰個位), 最頂嗰格係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>團體戰</strong></span>, 同<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同遊戲版本</strong></span>嘅朋友組好<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>四人小組</strong></span>後同其他四人小組對戰, 第二格係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Solo</strong></span><br />\nSplatfest期間無得同朋友合流<br />\n<br />\nQ: Fest Tee有咩特別?<br />\nA: Fest Tee拎去拆裝備碎片只需要$2000, 平時要$20000<br />\nFest Tee打Splatfest強制著上身, 完左Splatfest 就會系統回收<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>海螺</strong></span>有咩用?<br />\nA: 開裝備Slot (下面有詳細解釋)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 同Nintendo Switch Online App有咩連動?<br />\nA: 可以用App 開房 generate URL, Share URL俾其他人就可以join你<br />\n亦可<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">查看自己對戰之相關數據, 購買遊戲內之服裝</span></strong>, 以及進行語音通話<br />\n由於港服未開 iOS要用美/日ac search &quot;Nintendo Switch Online&quot; download<br />\nAndroid可用apk, download link: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.apkmirror.com/apk/nintendo-co-ltd/nintendo-switch-online/nintendo-switch-online-1-0-4-release/nintendo-switch-online-1-0-4-android-apk-download/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apkmirror.com%2Fapk%2Fnintendo-co-ltd%2Fnintendo-switch-online%2Fnintendo-switch-online-1-0-4-release%2Fnintendo-switch-online-1-0-4-android-apk-download%2F&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=c07f2c1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.apkmirror.com/apk/nintendo-co-ltd/nintendo-switch-online/nintendo-switch-online-1-0-4-release/nintendo-switch-online-1-0-4-android-apk-download/</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: 點<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>用App買衫</strong></span>?<br />\nA: Online對戰一次&gt;開App揀Splatoon2&gt;右上角Shop Icon&gt;揀衫落注文(落訂)&gt;入Game對戰屋(Lobby)隔離<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>海膽仔</strong></span>&gt;最後一個選項俾錢拎衫<br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>用App訂衫</strong></span>有無限幾時俾錢?<br />\nA: 好似無<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解衫分咁多牌子?<br />\nA: 各牌子對應一種服裝技能, 抽中該技能的機會 會有所提升<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/aJmum.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FaJmum.jpg&h=e6c60452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 隻<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">海膽仔</span></strong>咁多選項其實講緊乜?<br />\nA: 第一個係買廣場上啲人嘅衫(要事先買廣場上啲人訂購)<br />\n第二個係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>用海螺開裝備Slot</strong></span><br />\n第三個係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拆裝備碎片</strong></span><br />\n第四個係組合碎片<br />\n第五個係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>買用App訂嘅衫</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/aCPEz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FaCPEz.jpg&h=58c9cbbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57d3054f61a667ea8f82d052d965664c1f171646","tid":697300,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:07:35.000Z","msg":"Q: 點樣<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>舉報玩家</strong></span>(放置/自殘/Cheat等等...)?<br />\nA: App-&gt;戰績(格劍icon)-&gt;揀返嗰場-&gt;click佢個名-&gt;通報<br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Amiibo</strong></span>有咩用?<br />\nA: 可以解鎖衫,武器,歌等, 亦可儲存裝備配置 同埋可以進入影相模式<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFCqcd1XkAAL4eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFCqcd1XkAAL4eb.jpg&h=43dcf688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各Amiibo 解鎖嘅武器請睇依度:<br />\n<a href=\"https://splatoon2.gamepedia.jp/archives/2159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsplatoon2.gamepedia.jp%2Farchives%2F2159&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=bc10de6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://splatoon2.gamepedia.jp/archives/2159</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解scan Amiibo得個頭拎? 唔係有全身裝咩?<br />\nA: 先對戰超過20場&gt; X掣&gt; +掣&gt; Amiibo讀自己裝備&gt;去Amiibo Box拎其他裝備<br />\n<br />\nQ: Amiibo可唔可以借比人用<br />\nA: 可以, 但要係主機設定還原隻amiibo洗走所有資料, 建議拎曬衫先借比人<br />\n<br />\nQ: 可唔可以唔用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>體感</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 入設定(主城撳X-&gt;L)可以set唔用, 但真心建議俾次機會體感, 上手後自然同方便好多 <br />\n同埋注意體感係for你微調, 大幅度轉視角依然係靠右菇<br />\n<br />\nQ: 可唔可以set手提mode唔用體感, 桌上mode同TV mode用體感?<br />\nA: 可以, 手提同桌上&amp;TV mode係分開set<br />\n<br />\nQ: 對戰時點<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>傳送(飛)去隊友度</strong></span>?<br />\nA: X -&gt; 揀隊友 -&gt; A<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點出<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大絕</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 右上角儲滿氣按R3(右菇)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 武器隔離枝旗仔代表咩?<br />\nA: 熟練度, 到5嘅倍數會有Bonus經驗值<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有無需要買Pro手掣?<br />\nA: Pro手掣舒服好多但唔係必需<br />\n<br />\nQ: 視角怪怪地喎....?<br />\nA: Y掣Reset 視角<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>畫畫</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 主城紅色郵筒<br />\n<br />\nQ: Hero Mode (<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>單人劇情模式</strong></span>) 點入?<br />\nA: 主城左上拎遮個「啊婆」<br />\n<br />\nQ: Hero Mode d武器點升? 包唔包埋對戰mode?<br />\nA: 第一關門口個box。兩個mode嘅武器係分開<br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Salmon Run</strong></span> 點先有得online玩?<br />\nA: 指定時間(X掣-&gt;ステージ情報-&gt;Salmon Run有得睇,顯示時間係你本地時間)<br />\n去左上商會, 或者直接 X-&gt;商會<br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Salmon Run </strong></span>Mode奬品去邊度兌換?<br />\nA: 主城左上角市商會隔黎有部機<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>倍經/倍$卷</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 主城黃巴士<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點同FD一齊玩<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Salmon Run</strong></span> Mode?<br />\nA: Salmon Run Mode介面揀第二個開房, 叫FD揀第二個揀你個人仔入你間房, 齊人後開場, 唔夠4個人會幫你揾街外人入來<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有無得<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一機雙打</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 無<br />\n<br />\nQ: 邊度開<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>本地(Local)對戰</strong></span>場?<br />\nA: 去機鋪(イカッチャ, 主城右面), 第一個係揾房, 第二個係開房, 第三個係開Salmon Run 房<br />\n<br />\nQ: 一開Game叫你Set個性別同造型之後仲有無得換?<br />\nA: 主城撳X-&gt;R R R-&gt;最底(その他)-&gt;最底(プレイヤー設定)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有無連登Splatoon交友(<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>加朋友</strong></span>)區?<br />\nA: 有,<br />\n連登 Splatoon2 任豚登記表<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/cVBZKp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FcVBZKp&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=efbcbc3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/cVBZKp</a><br />\n<br />\n連登 Splatoon2 任豚名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/zmzkon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fzmzkon&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=9ecc9795\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/zmzkon</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">服裝技能</span></strong>中文翻譯(from 巴哈):<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7reG7y0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7reG7y0.png&h=ef4968eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31587&amp;snA=1730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D31587%26snA%3D1730&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=4786ef1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31587&amp;snA=1730</a>"},{"pid":"8bf23ce2c25c89f4ff01982af414d240d7ab6399","tid":697300,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:07:45.000Z","msg":"Q: <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Rank Mode (ガチマッチ) </span></strong>啲玩法係點架?<br />\nA: Rank mode有3款，三款各自有獨立ranking，都係由C-開始 <strong><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>by 景三巴打</em></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">運魚</span></strong>:地圖中央有枝魚炮，射爆佢個保護罩，就可以拎枝魚炮上身，自己武器就變成魚炮，魚炮可以儲力，將魚炮運去敵方陣地的小高台就嬴 (通常係重生點行出少少的位置)<br />\n畫面上方的數字係魚炮曾經運到有幾近小高台<br />\n有人拎起枝魚炮，畫面會有show個icon仔話你知條友係邊<br />\n敵方射爆保護罩爆開會死人，見到就爆唔好行咁近，邊隊射爆保護罩都可以搶拎魚炮，不過一爆就埋去搶好危險<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">搶地</span></strong>：地圖會有專有地區框起左，將成個框起的地方油到變成自己色就開始count down，count 到0就贏，被對方搶返會有罰秒<br />\n如果有兩個框起地區，要填晒兩個先開始count down<br />\n填完個地安全就留一兩個人，另外一兩個就出去填返對面的移動路線，反兜敵人or埋伏，唔好企死個框區等敵人到<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>推車/推塔</strong></span>：地圖中央有座塔，企上去就會自動行去敵方陣地，成功去到敵方陣地就贏，雙方都有人企係上面會唔郁<br />\n自方陣地時，企一企上去佢會自動返中央地帶，唔駛死企上面<br />\n越多人企上面行得越快，越易死晒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Salmon Run Mode常見問題</span></strong></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><em>由鑫毳巴打翻譯</em></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DH2dkWKUMAAAOsr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDH2dkWKUMAAAOsr.jpg&h=ee660316&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/StaySpla/status/895890149153820672\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStaySpla%2Fstatus%2F895890149153820672&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=500b548b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStaySpla%2Fstatus%2F895890149153820672&h=077bced1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/StaySpla/status/895890149153820672</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[三跑爬分常見問題]</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以下為一篇自稱640分　350％寫既三文魚跑要注意事項。<br />\n<br />\n首先，最先發覺既係<br />\n1.有人死好多<br />\n2.有人唔肯運金春<br />\n3.有人未理解到敵人優先解決順序<br />\n4.特別多人唔識對應UFO、飯盒<br />\n5.未理解到武器特性、大技既應用<br />\n6.動作唔流暢、唔識分工<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【死太多】</span></strong><br />\n街場通常都總係有d人會不斷死，為全隊勝利著想狗衝上前打特殊三文魚然後就死，依種情況當然唔得，除左拖時間跳海自殺之外你死多過４、５次請你自己理解為拖後腿。我認為玩三跑係需要超認真既合作，你走一條友就等於隊友要做1.3份量工作，基本走位「唔好亂鳩衝，牽制住慢慢支援隊友」既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【唔運春】</span></strong><br />\n其實結果畫面唔可以判斷到依咩野，但我睇得出有班人係唔會運春。如果運春既數譏差成15以上既話根本就係你差唔多無做過野。除左有煩膠出現之外，運春係一件好重要既野。但太過睇重運春既話又會令到生存同埋輔助方面減弱，所以都要諗埋其他方面。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【優先次序】</strong></span><br />\n單刀直入<br />\n垃圾桶&rarr;塔&rarr;遮&rarr;炸彈＝蛇&rarr;車&rarr;鯊<br />\n垃圾桶雖然一個人都打得死，但通常都係複數出現，搵多幾件友就打得快，塔放置Play佢好快就會顏射到你好快完場，請善用大技快快手打死佢，槍打到既就打，遮可以反射就反射，都係唔得既話就圍死佢，炸彈就請遠距既人打，短撚就幫手油腳比個位佢射，蛇如果去到Container執邊就好Q麻煩，所以請快快手搞死佢。鯊同落雨好易係混戰時執你雞補你刀，唔好唔理佢。雖然殺係好易，但有多時間既話，請引佢地去個Container執邊先殺。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【特殊關卡】</strong></span><br />\n開波前５秒其實睇浪可以知水位準備升定降。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【武器特性】</strong></span><br />\n狙<br />\n專打炸彈，之後就運春，夜晚就用大砲。<br />\n<br />\n長槍<br />\n基本上同狙差唔多，但比起狙你更方便對應塔。<br />\n<br />\n短撚<br />\n秒塔、打細怪、打炸彈以外大魚、油地。<br />\n<br />\nRoller<br />\n主要打細怪，但打塔同炸彈唔係你個行，打其他啦。<br />\n<br />\nBlaster<br />\n打塔都叫OK，其他普通，打細怪又唔痛。　<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>大技方面</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n著地：<br />\n混戰時救全隊<br />\n<br />\n高壓顏射槍：<br />\n除左炸彈以外都可以殺到<br />\n塔無開槍時可以射頭爆死<br />\n<br />\n飛行背包：<br />\n含家死晒時可以飛上空中避難。<br />\n<br />\nBomb rush：<br />\n清怪<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【當自己玩緊單機】</strong></span><br />\n除左回收春、捨身清遠處大怪以外單機打野多數仆街。<br />\n如果隊友運緊春得你自己一個，請你諗下自己係咪一個打到而又唔會死先，<br />\n知唔夠打既你幫手運春等埋隊友好過你SOLO。<br />\n<br />\n雖然篇野好長，但多謝各位睇到依度。<br />\n將心比心，請諗下各位隊友既處境先。"},{"pid":"5ef4818a6b352f4ae176551048bfad0369d58c45","tid":697300,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:08:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Salmon Run Mode 心得</span></strong></span> <div style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><em>by夜闌人靜巴打</em></strong></div><br />\n個人認為打工需要一個主力清怪輸出，另一個負責執蛋(特別潮漲時D怪多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，當然要視乎武器池抽到咩武器，例如毛筆執蛋、中碳清怪。<br />\n<br />\n運蛋方面，高難度場要習慣打完BOSS後拿一粒蛋就走，唔好戀戰或折返原處執蛋(除非蛋在籠附近)，因為呢個時候另一邊已經有BOSS(頻密既鳴笛聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )出現等你揾佢。如果發現那個WAVE 垃圾桶頻繁重生就留單邊垃圾桶，三角炸彈消耗太多墨水導致效率降低。<br />\n<br />\n另外好似[97]的範例片，一開局所有boss(除左垃圾桶同高塔)最好等它們自己走到接近屋企附近才解近，減少整體運蛋所需時間亦同時減低危險性。特別開局是雨傘時<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，全員要一齊站在籠附近誘導佢自己飛近，被它瞄準的人可以嘗試把氣球發射角度成一直線打回去。至於鐵板車同地鼠(送蛋BOSS)無論開局到完場，都要把它們引回籠附近解決，有時通關與否就取決於它們。潮退時等BOSS走到岸口位置再打，太前打BOSS路口過窄危險性太高，不是被兵圍剿就是被拍落水，同時執蛋也不方便。<br />\n<br />\n以下有幾個地點需要注意<br />\n1.難破船右邊升降機位置<br />\n<img src=\"http://splatoonsokuhou.site/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/aHR0cHM6Ly9kb3R1cC5vcmcvdXBsb2RhL2RvdHVwLm9yZzEzNTk1MTMuanBn-1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsplatoonsokuhou.site%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2FaHR0cHM6Ly9kb3R1cC5vcmcvdXBsb2RhL2RvdHVwLm9yZzEzNTk1MTMuanBn-1.jpeg&h=8a82879d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每個wave 開局或完場前把升降機的牆油好，避免來不及搭升降機時也能爬牆回家。這個位置盡量也不要跳下去打怪，開局如果發現三個人都跳下去的話自己就要留在船上。儘管其餘兩個出怪方向平靜(好快就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，最多在船上放三角炸彈支援。<br />\n2.集落場前方鐵絲網<br />\n<img src=\"http://ga-m.com/image/news/2017/08/23/splatoon2-manta-maria-bubble-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fga-m.com%2Fimage%2Fnews%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2Fsplatoon2-manta-maria-bubble-10.jpg&h=3291a4e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除左開局，最需留單邊垃圾桶的位置。出現高塔時，拿了機動性高的武器(雙槍、毛筆、輕碳等等)需主動去清理。所有boss(除左垃圾桶同高塔)要等到它們上岸才解決。<br />\n3.工房退潮時<br />\n<img src=\"http://splatoon-nawabari.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/DPYrOUAV4AAKOfT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsplatoon-nawabari.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2FDPYrOUAV4AAKOfT.jpg&h=7bebd489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n把籠附近的地方油滿，籠後方的地、每條柱之間也需要油一油，走位逃生之用。如無必要不要走到鐵絲網，試過全員在那處翻艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。一樣引怪到籠附近解決。<br />\n4.シェケナダム鐵絲網<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-cc9CB9dw8Mw/WXar6rfqhOI/AAAAAAACk-s/U7TVnRx8DmULl-8px0_fYShvzYneC1ULgCLcBGAs/s1600/2017072320284100-C616B031331154665D639EF16DA76BC0_x562.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-cc9CB9dw8Mw%2FWXar6rfqhOI%2FAAAAAAACk-s%2FU7TVnRx8DmULl-8px0_fYShvzYneC1ULgCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F2017072320284100-C616B031331154665D639EF16DA76BC0_x562.jpg&h=eab24ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開局前除左油高台既牆之外，鐵絲網附近既所有牆都油一油，逃跑之用。同樣開局引怪到籠附近解決。BTW，金魚水閥如果係鐵絲網個邊開中就等它走離鐵絲網才攻擊，太遠打執蛋費時之餘，金魚也越走越快(鐵絲網上)導致不能令它爆蛋。<br />\n<br />\n金魚水閥(間欠泉 )可以參考下圖<br />\n難破船ドン・ブラコ Marooner's Bay<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.atwikiimg.com/www65.atwiki.jp/ikachang2/attach/17/218/Aカンケツ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.atwikiimg.com%2Fwww65.atwiki.jp%2Fikachang2%2Fattach%2F17%2F218%2FA%E3%82%AB%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B1%E3%83%841.jpg&h=15263e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海上集落シャケト場 Lost Outpost<br />\n<img src=\"http://splatoon-nawabari.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/DIFqGdxU0AAHyn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsplatoon-nawabari.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2FDIFqGdxU0AAHyn6.jpg&h=1b252980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nトキシラズいぶし工房 Salmonid Smokeyard<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.atwikiimg.com/www65.atwiki.jp/ikachang2/attach/17/214/kanketu4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.atwikiimg.com%2Fwww65.atwiki.jp%2Fikachang2%2Fattach%2F17%2F214%2Fkanketu4.jpg&h=6a028acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nシェケナダム Spawning Grounds<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DLlNF4uUMAAgvkr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDLlNF4uUMAAgvkr.jpg&h=d917ee8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大絕方面，感覺到場面就快會亂到不受控制或蛋數目嚴重不足時，唔理WAVE1 WAVE2都照開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n噴射背包(複數長蛇、高塔、爆彈、垃圾桶)<br />\n高壓水槍(兩個或以上既BOSS時使用、複數垃圾桶、遠處高塔、救遠處人用)<br />\n英雄落地(主要爆彈)<br />\nBomb Launcher(籠附近多怪時、高塔、複數地鼠、救全家用)<br />\n<br />\n幾個要點<br />\nsalmon run 油牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對比油地更重要<br />\n誘導BOSS 拉近籠再打<br />\n留意有冇隊友變水泡<br />\n留意時間及還需要收集的蛋數目<br />\n打完BOSS執一粒蛋就揾下一個BOSS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當成為垃圾桶或高塔目標時遠離隊友<br />\n蛋收集數目達成後就遠離隊友，唔好痴埋一齊瘋狂執蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n金魚暴走時爬牆達致延遲效果"},{"pid":"32d2902fb387c26ab30b2afac371a34ce6ad84ba","tid":697300,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:08:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">合流刷錢大法</span></strong></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><em>by鑫毳巴打</em></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C_XiIUkUQAQdR0s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC_XiIUkUQAQdR0s.jpg&h=336607db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">(圖文不符)</span></span></div><br />\n刷錢企位推薦<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1pBXEJDsU867hxYmF2hL1L4BGdxittfX4s8xn1AyvQXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1pBXEJDsU867hxYmF2hL1L4BGdxittfX4s8xn1AyvQXU%2F&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=464fee7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1pBXEJDsU867hxYmF2hL1L4BGdxittfX4s8xn1AyvQXU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">基本玩法：</span></strong><br />\n以一位巴打做中心，其他玩家就輪住合流個位巴打。<br />\n合流輪候應該只有3個、4個空位，<br />\n所以需要3、4場等街外人走場先可以再輪流入房。<br />\n當房中有六個左右就可以正式刷錢。<br />\n<br />\n消耗時間約3分鐘1局，相比起RANK 5分鐘快<br />\n而且理論上唔需要在意理勝負都有幾好既回報。<br />\n但一直輸都有d唔公平，所以我都希望加個機制，<br />\n防止有巴打開幕時周圍油地博取最後1000分。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>基本計錢公式：</strong></span><br />\n(油地分數 + 勝利額外1000分 ) x 1.5 = 錢<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n暫時刷錢最有效率方法摸摸當中<br />\n以下為我刷錢最高紀錄3550分建議<br />\n<br />\n1.企空礦地方<br />\n2.雙方無高低差<br />\n3.雙方距離為射距多丁丁<br />\n4.唔好移動 左右Fing住油  <br />\n5.Fing角度自己感覺一下，可以留意右上角數字加得快唔快，慢慢調節角度速度。<br />\n6.潛0.1秒即起身油幾滴，1至2秒潛1下0.1秒，盡量做到無油時剛剛回滿大技。<br />\n7.以大技為回油方式，但唔用技繼續主武器油。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>注意事項：</strong></span><br />\n1.未齊人/未劫房前，請認真正常玩。<br />\n2.需要趕人時，慢慢油密d自己屋企，見到人就走，你懂的。<br />\n3.有街外人搗亂時，街外人隊請油少d路，方面巴打們警覺街外人位置圍射排外。<br />\n4.入場機中萬中無一，請盡量穿著三星裝備，無時間比你出去洗裝。<br />\n5.場地一轉就完，為巴打們著想請盡量打到尾。 <br />\n<br />\n互射方式+無油時處理方法　　<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要點：Keep shooting</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/13KHi12zUq4GWc/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F13KHi12zUq4GWc%2Fgiphy.gif&h=e4003ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n錯誤示範(請睇對方)　停手一秒鐘　你同對手銀包就各少左50蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/7Zv0Rzg18C0dG/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F7Zv0Rzg18C0dG%2Fgiphy.gif&h=e58f5473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遲下後補建議企位，仲摸索當中。"},{"pid":"9c5daf1950d54281718fe61ec0e34b9093243180","tid":697300,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:08:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">另類玩法: 私人房歡樂場</span></strong></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><em>by鑫毳巴打</em></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">捉迷藏</span></strong></span></div><br />\n遊戲模式：地盤戰 (Turf War)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>玩法介紹:</strong></span><br />\n以1v4進行，全員限定用毛筆或相同射程武器，<br />\n避免射程差距令部份位置捉唔到唔公平。<br />\n禁止使用任何SP或副武器，除左花灑。<br />\n4位逃走參賽者(下稱人)可以利用頭1分鐘不斷油地誤導然後搵位潛。<br />\n頭1分鐘內 捉人一方(下稱鬼)只可以背向重生點<br />\n自律唔望地圖唔望向賽區<br />\n當倒數時間到2:00就可以開始捉<br />\n人可以逃走可以不斷油，<br />\n比人殺左就企重生點唔準離開<br />\n若果錯手殺鬼請自行SuperJump重生點當或自殺<br />\n全滅就輸。<br />\n相反倒數完就鬼輸。<br />\n<br />\n好處：熟悉地圖細小地方，Shortcut或埋伏地點之類。<br />\n壞處：無錢收。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全員逃走中</span></strong></span></div><br />\n遊戲模式：地盤戰 (Turf War)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>玩法介紹:</strong></span><br />\n以4v4進行，武器使用不限定，<br />\n一隊Hunter，一隊逃走。。<br />\n禁止使用任何SP。<br />\n4位逃走參賽可以利用頭30秒不斷擴大自己可移動位置。<br />\nHunter重生點待機，2:30開波。<br />\n<br />\n跟捉迷藏一樣。<br />\n人可以逃走可以不斷油，<br />\n比人殺左就企重生點唔準離開<br />\n全滅就輸。<br />\n相反倒數完就Hunter輸。<br />\n一樣錯手殺Hunter請自行死番重生點。<br />\n<br />\n而Hunter就只可以射擊時移動，只可以用主武器。<br />\n回墨就原地回。<br />\n<br />\n好處：提高生存率，熟讀地圖角落。<br />\n壞處：無錢收。"},{"pid":"207f46c1a2acbdd258324f9ac3c835824603cce7","tid":697300,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:08:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">實戰技巧</span></span></strong></div><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><em>by 鑫毳巴打</em></strong></div>  <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DHjrWKbVwAADbnP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDHjrWKbVwAADbnP.png&h=3725ef44&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">多圖小心爆數據</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1D8_UzaAKmP4a6pMJPvVYS93-CxDAHmD_6F_AZ4nzrIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1D8_UzaAKmP4a6pMJPvVYS93-CxDAHmD_6F_AZ4nzrIE%2F&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=2b018ed7\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1D8_UzaAKmP4a6pMJPvVYS93-CxDAHmD_6F_AZ4nzrIE/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Salmon Run教學/相關資訊/武器心得 </span></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><em>by 矢作萌花巴打</em></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFOvO9YVYAEfgTp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFOvO9YVYAEfgTp.jpg&h=1c99678d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1lW9ZS876IwGSLzaLUJoPHF6D-xEdxT6SlHKhzGloadc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1lW9ZS876IwGSLzaLUJoPHF6D-xEdxT6SlHKhzGloadc%2F&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=919da760\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1lW9ZS876IwGSLzaLUJoPHF6D-xEdxT6SlHKhzGloadc/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">裝備選擇心得及其入手方法與海螺相關</span></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><em>by 鑫毳巴打</em></strong></div>  <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DF1hLKvUMAA4FEN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDF1hLKvUMAA4FEN.jpg&h=48933cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Cdi64Q8yr5A-YjZplNA4CKno6AW-MJVPer5Cva7Fn5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1Cdi64Q8yr5A-YjZplNA4CKno6AW-MJVPer5Cva7Fn5Y%2F&d=TUG5Lz16rKvZQ3HvMbV9KkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=18cd94a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Cdi64Q8yr5A-YjZplNA4CKno6AW-MJVPer5Cva7Fn5Y/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><